<br />\nMcKinley高中合唱團曾有過輝煌的過去，他們是這個領域中的佼佼者。隨著歲月的流逝，合唱團緋聞不斷，醜聞纏身，很多富有才華的年輕人都悄然離開了。現在，這個合唱團成了&ldquo;南郭先生&rdquo;和孤僻學生的&ldquo;避風港&rdquo;。生性樂觀的Will接受了校長交辦的這項艱鉅任務：重塑McKingley合唱團的形象，創造另一次輝煌。 Will並不孤獨－－因為他有漂亮女教師Emma Pillsbury（Jayma Mays扮演）的全力輔佐<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=oIln4n8eGtpJdUtBmG8i3l0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=ca8d557a\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=oIln4n8eGtpJdUtBmG8i3l0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=7cb42fc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e16429ad6242fa2ffe46ca4daf85e5961bf606b","tid":583104,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T17:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a54c6163f0f47d74fa6d18856501c51799a69c","tid":583104,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T19:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e447cad17711fb437e436221f54e76bc59bb32","tid":583104,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T19:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid